WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 3=

00:00:05.060 --> 00:00:05.980
(It hurts...)

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:07.899
(I can feel my leg again?)

00:00:07.900 --> 00:00:09.019
(How is this possible?)

00:00:09.020 --> 00:00:10.819
The Imperial Preceptor was incompetent.

00:00:10.820 --> 00:00:12.260
Everything he said was nonsense.

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:14.020
It's okay, Father.

00:00:14.140 --> 00:00:16.379
Now that you've taken me in,

00:00:16.380 --> 00:00:18.500
your doom

00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:23.459
is coming.

00:00:23.460 --> 00:00:24.619
What are you talking about?

00:00:24.620 --> 00:00:25.539
Please don't, Princess.

00:00:25.540 --> 00:00:26.539
Come down now.

00:00:26.540 --> 00:00:27.460
Be good.

00:00:27.860 --> 00:00:28.860
Good girl.

00:00:30.740 --> 00:00:31.859
Come with me to the study.

00:00:31.860 --> 00:00:33.939
Why the study?

00:00:33.940 --> 00:00:36.059
If I'm hungry,

00:00:36.060 --> 00:00:38.500
shouldn't we be going
to the kitchen instead?

00:00:39.180 --> 00:00:41.099
I'm human now.

00:00:41.100 --> 00:00:43.940
I can't survive
on spiritual energy alone anymore.

00:00:44.700 --> 00:00:45.540
Let's go.

00:00:56.460 --> 00:00:57.660
Did you see that just now?

00:00:57.940 --> 00:00:58.660
Shi,

00:00:58.820 --> 00:01:01.259
wasn't the little princess saying

00:01:01.260 --> 00:01:03.540
that His Highness's hard days
are finally over?

00:01:03.940 --> 00:01:05.139
Dajun,

00:01:05.140 --> 00:01:07.180
you always miss the point.

00:01:07.820 --> 00:01:09.780
It's been three years,

00:01:10.820 --> 00:01:12.580
and this is the first time

00:01:12.620 --> 00:01:15.779
I've seen His Highness smile so happily.

00:01:15.780 --> 00:01:16.900
His Highness smiled?

00:01:17.060 --> 00:01:18.700
Of course he did.
You just didn't notice.

00:01:19.140 --> 00:01:19.940
I don't care.

00:01:20.060 --> 00:01:21.379
From today onward,

00:01:21.380 --> 00:01:24.300
everything the little princess
says is right.

00:01:26.420 --> 00:01:27.980
Little Princess,

00:01:28.220 --> 00:01:30.300
I'll go make something
delicious for you right now!

00:01:30.820 --> 00:01:31.980
Kitchen helpers!

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:36.440
(Prince Jing Manor)

00:01:49.220 --> 00:01:50.060
Jinx!

00:01:51.100 --> 00:01:51.939
Jinx!

00:01:51.940 --> 00:01:52.499
Stay away!

00:01:52.500 --> 00:01:52.779
Jinx!

00:01:52.780 --> 00:01:53.419
It's you!

00:01:53.420 --> 00:01:54.339
Jinx!

00:01:54.340 --> 00:01:55.059
Beat him to death!

00:01:55.060 --> 00:01:56.499
- You're the one who brought this disaster.
- Jinx!

00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:57.259
Useless cripple!

00:01:57.260 --> 00:01:59.259
Give me back my son's life!

00:01:59.260 --> 00:02:00.739
Thirty thousand soldiers!

00:02:00.740 --> 00:02:02.500
You got them all killed!

00:02:03.340 --> 00:02:05.699
Not one of those
thirty thousand soldiers survived.

00:02:05.700 --> 00:02:08.059
Why did you make it back alive?

00:02:08.060 --> 00:02:08.659
Get out!

00:02:08.660 --> 00:02:09.579
Yeah!

00:02:09.580 --> 00:02:10.700
Why should you live?

00:02:11.220 --> 00:02:12.539
Give me back my son's life!

00:02:12.540 --> 00:02:13.500
Jinx!

00:02:14.460 --> 00:02:15.700
You're nothing but useless trash!

00:02:26.540 --> 00:02:27.900
Mother...

00:02:30.320 --> 00:02:31.639
(Consort Shu)
A cursed lone star.

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:32.600
(Noble Consort of Tianxuan Kingdom)

00:02:32.600 --> 00:02:34.200
You bring ruin
to your family and your lord.

00:02:35.940 --> 00:02:37.439
How dare you come back here?

00:02:37.440 --> 00:02:39.299
(Xiao Changming,
Emperor of Tianxuan Kingdom)

00:02:39.300 --> 00:02:40.619
As long as you live,

00:02:40.620 --> 00:02:42.739
more people will die because of you.

00:02:42.740 --> 00:02:45.020
This is your fate!

00:03:03.540 --> 00:03:06.060
I died so miserably...

00:03:06.420 --> 00:03:08.580
Give me back my life...

00:03:08.780 --> 00:03:11.220
Give me back my life...

00:03:32.460 --> 00:03:33.259
Father.

00:03:33.260 --> 00:03:35.420
I will chase
the bad things away for you.

00:03:39.100 --> 00:03:40.580
(This is...)

00:03:41.580 --> 00:03:42.900
(Feeling.)

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:08.280
(Prince Jing Manor)

00:04:13.380 --> 00:04:16.140
Looks like I
really picked the right meal ticket.

00:04:16.740 --> 00:04:19.220
Now this is what living should be like.

00:04:28.780 --> 00:04:29.780
Father.

00:04:30.300 --> 00:04:32.540
You don't like me, do you?

00:04:33.460 --> 00:04:34.419
When have I ever...

00:04:34.420 --> 00:04:36.459
If you don't like me, just say it.

00:04:36.460 --> 00:04:38.660
You don't have to scheme
to drive me away like this.

00:04:38.940 --> 00:04:39.859
Try it yourself.

00:04:39.860 --> 00:04:40.899
It's awful.

00:04:40.900 --> 00:04:42.099
You've ruined my appetite.

00:04:42.100 --> 00:04:42.940
Bad review.

00:04:50.940 --> 00:04:52.620
What's wrong with this fish?

00:04:53.180 --> 00:04:55.020
Could someone have poisoned it?

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:06.359
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:05:06.360 --> 00:05:10.199
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:10.200 --> 00:05:13.719
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:13.720 --> 00:05:16.680
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:05:17.560 --> 00:05:21.199
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:05:21.200 --> 00:05:24.960
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:28.359
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:28.360 --> 00:05:32.400
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:41.679
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:45.319
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:45.320 --> 00:05:49.039
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:52.679
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:52.680 --> 00:05:56.359
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:58.279
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:05:58.280 --> 00:06:04.480
♪Good fortune♪